<p>Copy and paste the names you find to unload the ftdi devices</p>

<p>sudo kextunload -b com.FTDI.driver.FTDIUSBSerialDriver</p>

<p>sudo kextunload -b com.apple.driver.AppleUSBFTDI</p>

